.Dt SMSCPHY 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm smscphy
.Nd SMSC LAN87xx 10/100 Ethernet PHYs
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "smscphy* at mii? phy ?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver supports SMSC LAN8700, LAN8710, and LAN8720 10/100 Ethernet PHYs.
